text:
It has lovely, well maintained campus ground n koi pond.  The aircon food court has many good food stalls at good value (much cheaper than foodcourts in typical malls).
Like the cleanliness n spaciousness.  There's a roadside field just before ITE building where I spotted 2 lovely migratory birds this morning...hope they drop by again:)
Ps. there's also a nice big air-conditioned Sheng siong, much cleaner than other outlets. Also a small Popular bk store n First Culinary, a popular chinese restaurant.

It is the HQ of the three ITE Colleges.It has two canteens, one Chinese restaurant (open to public ),several fast food outlets ( open to public ).It also has a running track with football field and a swimming pool.There is an old commercial airplane outside the mid section of a building for practical sessions for the aero engineering course students.There are many different courses for students to enrol in.
Dated : 08/10/2017 ( Sunday ).
Another honoured alumni of ITE, unable to control himself  and using random violence against member of public.
The food there is the best... many shops to visit including a necessary atm service.
